<li>Keep your body straight from head to knees, engaging your core for stability.</li>



<li>Slowly bend your elbows, lowering your chest toward your hands while keeping elbows close to your sides.</li>



<li>Pause briefly at the bottom to intensify muscle activation.</li>



<li>Push through your palms to return to the starting position.</li>
</ol>



<h4 class="wp-block-heading">Tips&nbsp;</h4>



<ul>
<li>Keep elbows close to your body throughout to maximize tricep engagement.</li>



<li>Lower your body slowly to increase tension on the triceps.</li>



